41dff89fcd97a","tid":2423643,"uid":51271,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T04:41:36.000Z","msg":"匈牙利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T06:24:32.000Z","msg":"唔會系樓主咁唸發展囉。<br />\n旅遊業是越多人能入境越好<br />\n這樣就有三種情況<br />\n1只接受歐盟認證入境<br />\n2 只接受非歐盟認證入境<br />\n3) both<br />\n好明顯歐洲國家只會選1和3<br />\n如果疫苗前題是有效<br />\n3的國家肯定比1有利好多。<br />\n1只是綁死自己做少好多生意，除非非歐認證疫苗完全無效，對接受非歐盟認證也入境國家做成大量感染。<br />\n呢樣都會限死中國疫苗遊客只能去呢幾個歐國家玩，其他地方就執輸左。"},{"pid":"862a2077bc13ccaede6d3051af6b77fb61dbd97f","tid":2423643,"uid":40267,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T06:26:45.000Z","msg":"笑撚左<br />\n你估班歐豬會嫌錢腥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後咪死死地氣放佢地入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eefa8e50050fc1f03c51669a6a52b3707086a1ab","tid":2423643,"uid":301820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T06:27:09.000Z","msg":"匈牙利表示：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6d2f70d83b0cd1cc7ad16436635869af57d668","tid":2423643,"uid":13303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"97db44ff83a2d818399cd096f46ae8258bf48e5c","tid":2423643,"uid":32391,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e434588ecad2569504ed8444eae699348fe46a68","tid":2423643,"uid":305358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T04:57:40.000Z","msg":"打科興的廢老：我淨係想快D通關番大灣區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:42:31.000Z","msg":"就算係大陸都一直無講過打左科興就可以返大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T06:27:57.000Z","msg":"沃門未打都開關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />根本係你無就得 唔關有冇打針事"},{"pid":"db82b9e02ec1bb6a3038c5687d8876f21460a89d","tid":2423643,"uid":1525